@startuml State_Onboarding
title Feature 09 - Onboarding Flow State Machine

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #141417
    FontColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #333333
    ArrowColor #FF5C00
}

[*] --> Welcome : Sign-up complete

Welcome : Show value proposition
Welcome : "Let's get started" CTA
Welcome --> ConnectBank : User clicks CTA

ConnectBank : Security assurances
ConnectBank : Plaid Link button
ConnectBank --> PlaidLink : User clicks\n"Connect with Plaid"

PlaidLink : Plaid Link modal open
PlaidLink : User selects bank,\nenters credentials
PlaidLink --> ConnectBank : User cancels
PlaidLink --> Scanning : Plaid Link success\n/ save access token

Scanning : Animated progress
Scanning : Poll sync status
Scanning : "Analyzing transactions..."
Scanning --> Discovery : Sync complete\n/ subscriptions detected

Discovery : Hero savings number
Discovery : Summary cards
Discovery : "Review & Save" CTA
Discovery --> ActionApproval : User clicks CTA

ActionApproval : Grouped action list
ActionApproval : Approve/dismiss per item
ActionApproval : "Approve All" button
ActionApproval --> Complete : User clicks\n"Go to Dashboard"

Complete : Set user.status = 'active'
Complete --> [*] : Redirect to /dashboard

@enduml
